data.description:
NO CITY TAXES!!!! Charming 3 bed, 2 bath home in Alvarado, TX – a perfect blend of comfort and style! This well-maintained residence boasts a spacious open floor plan, creating an inviting atmosphere for family gatherings and entertaining friends. The kitchen features modern
 appliances, ample counter space, and a convenient breakfast bar. The master bedroom offers a tranquil retreat with an ensuite bathroom, providing privacy and relaxation.Enjoy the Texas sunshine in the expansive backyard, ideal for outdoor activities and hosting barbecues. The neighborhood is known for its friendly community and proximity to schools, parks, and local amenities. With easy access to highways, commuting is a breeze.
